  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/8f1400ef446c07193ecd674e2ec69747.poster.avif?t=1638622326\" width=550 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/8f1400ef446c07193ecd674e2ec69747.webm?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/8f1400ef446c07193ecd674e2ec69747.mp4?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Snatch Media Toolbox contains a Radio Stream Player with Gif Visuals, Audio Player with Search, MP4 Screensaver, Screen Recorder:  60fps, WebCam Viewer, File Converter and Timer.<br><br>Features<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Desktop Screen Recorder 60fps MKV with its own audio device, for quick start up<br></li><li>Video and Audio Converter for MP4 to MP3, MKV to MP4 60fps, any audio to mp3<br></li><li>Recording Timer controls all aspects of the toolbox<br></li><li>Audio Media Player, plays mp3, aac, flac, wav, ogg, aiff and m4a formats. Save your whole music collection and convert to playlists or use the Jukebox. <br></li><li>Radio Stream Player with Transitional Gif images & Recorder: MP3 an M3U8 Streams. Over 40 International Radio Stations or simply import your own stations. <br></li><li>GifPlayer plays multiple random gifs while your music or radio plays<br></li><li>Video Loop Screensaver plays multiple video loops while your music or radio plays<br></li><li>WebCam Viewer</li></ul><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/10de03228f4d03030c6aafbfcefad5c1.poster.avif?t=1638622326\" width=274 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/10de03228f4d03030c6aafbfcefad5c1.webm?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/10de03228f4d03030c6aafbfcefad5c1.mp4?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/dce3f59be3c7493d3913cf8741cac8b5.poster.avif?t=1638622326\" width=274 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/dce3f59be3c7493d3913cf8741cac8b5.webm?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/dce3f59be3c7493d3913cf8741cac8b5.mp4?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Snatch Media Toolbox Radio... Helping you to keep up with the very latest News and Music from your part of the world and every other.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/8f1400ef446c07193ecd674e2ec69747.poster.avif?t=1638622326\" width=550 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/8f1400ef446c07193ecd674e2ec69747.webm?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/8f1400ef446c07193ecd674e2ec69747.mp4?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Snatch Media Toolbox contains a Radio Stream Player with Gif Visuals, Audio Player with Search, MP4 Screensaver, Screen Recorder:  60fps, WebCam Viewer, File Converter and Timer.<br><br>Features<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Desktop Screen Recorder 60fps MKV with its own audio device, for quick start up<br></li><li>Video and Audio Converter for MP4 to MP3, MKV to MP4 60fps, any audio to mp3<br></li><li>Recording Timer controls all aspects of the toolbox<br></li><li>Audio Media Player, plays mp3, aac, flac, wav, ogg, aiff and m4a formats. Save your whole music collection and convert to playlists or use the Jukebox. <br></li><li>Radio Stream Player with Transitional Gif images & Recorder: MP3 an M3U8 Streams. Over 40 International Radio Stations or simply import your own stations. <br></li><li>GifPlayer plays multiple random gifs while your music or radio plays<br></li><li>Video Loop Screensaver plays multiple video loops while your music or radio plays<br></li><li>WebCam Viewer</li></ul><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/10de03228f4d03030c6aafbfcefad5c1.poster.avif?t=1638622326\" width=274 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/10de03228f4d03030c6aafbfcefad5c1.webm?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/10de03228f4d03030c6aafbfcefad5c1.mp4?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/dce3f59be3c7493d3913cf8741cac8b5.poster.avif?t=1638622326\" width=274 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/dce3f59be3c7493d3913cf8741cac8b5.webm?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716280/extras/dce3f59be3c7493d3913cf8741cac8b5.mp4?t=1638622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Snatch Media Toolbox Radio... Helping you to keep up with the very latest News and Music from your part of the world and every other.",
